pageTitle: Midwest Dairy Council and Land O’Lakes Award Six Iowa Schools with Pro Football, Cheese Prize Packages | Hoards Dairyman
TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {8516=Wings Park Elementary in Oelwein, Iowa, was awarded the contest’s grand prize, including a visit from a pro football alumni player, a $2,500 cash donation from the GENYOUth Foundation, and pro football player-signed merchandise for their school and chosen hero. The prize was awarded for their video creation about a “cheesy” meal or snack that celebrates a local hero. Former Minnesota Vikings outside linebacker, Matt Blair #59, is visiting the school today (Friday, May 10)., 6591=5.10.2013}
